<Base page="Resume">
  <div>    
    <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem">
      <p>
        I currently lead engineering at Elyos in London.
      </p>
        <p>
        My passion is leading high performing engineering teams, small or large, owning complex technical systems. I've spent most of my career in regulated industries like healthcare and finance, balancing technical innovation with regulatory rigour.
        </p>
      <p>
        While I enjoy the strategy and mentoring element I'm not afraid of getting my hands dirty shipping enterprise code in a wide variety of languages, frameworks and cloud providers - across frontend, backend, infrastructure, AI/data platforms and hardware.
      </p>
      <p>
        Outside of work I love travel, food (especially all things{' '}
        <a target="_blank" href="/2021/08/26/sandwich-loaf">bread</a>{' '}
        and{' '}
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/BpZW1b4HE5m/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">pastry</a>), and{' '}
        <a href="https://twitter.com/mnbbrown/status/1487054469770612737?s=20&t=BjnBvytvzqHdeyzNXJfBHA" 
           target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">aviation</a>{' '}
